title: Former NSW premier Mike Baird joins NAB
text:
Tue, Feb 28, 2017, 12:29 PM NZDT - New Zealand Markets close in 4 hrs 31 mins Former NSW premier Mike Baird joins NAB AAP – 31 minutes ago View Photo 

Former NSW premier Mike Baird is joining National Australia Bank as chief customer officer for the lender's corporate and institutional banking unit. 
Mr Baird retired unexpectedly from politics in January to spend more time with his family. 
NAB's statement to the Australian Securities Exchange says Mr Baird, who previously worked for the bank, will take up his new job in April.   Trump seeks 'historic increase' in defence AAP
